Maybe you won't be soloing red-to-60 mobs, but so what? PoP doesn't have the same balance as pre-Pop did.  Just because a mob is red does not necessarily mean that the mob is stronger.  I know level 65ish mobs in PoN that drop nothing for loot and give crap exp compared to fighting other mobs.  There are level 61 giants in PoP that hit for 700+.  Red, for once, no longer means phat lewts and uber exp.<br>
<br>
